beer.beer_description:
Combining our creative expertise with Sydney based record label EtcEtc, we've created the perfect summer beer in this super sized DDH Pacific Ale.
Dry hopped with Galaxy and thiol enriched Mega Motueka hops, built over a base of premium ale malt, wheat malt and a touch of malted oats for a light haze, fluffy mouthfeel and low bitterness.
Sound Wave was crafted for beach goers, music enthusiasts and beer lovers. 
Our partnership is a fusion of creativity & shared passions and is a testament to the tasty outcomes achievable when great minds collaborate. Celebrating the sun, the sea and the harmonious spirit of music and beer down under
